title: So You Think You Can Dance Australia S01E01.avi
description:
So You Think You Can Dance Australia is here!

So You Think You Can Dance Australia has arrived! 

Rogue Traders frontwoman, former Neighbours femme fatale and now host of So You Think You Can Dance Australia Natalie Bassingthwaighte will be joined by a stellar judging panel including international producer and acclaimed choreographer Bonnie Lythgoe, events guru and choreographer Jason Coleman and one of Australia?s brightest dancing talents and choreographer Matt Lee.
